4" data-scroll-anchor="true" data-turn="assistant" style="min-height: calc(-248px + 100dvh);"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT 說：</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pb-10 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="49f891d4-a022-499c-92b3-269c5c551733" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1" data-turn-start-message="true" tabindex="0"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="135">No worries — this part is a bit confusing if you’ve never uploaded to GitHub before 👍<br data-start="86" data-end="89">
I’ll guide you <strong data-start="104" data-end="134">step-by-step (very simple)</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="137" data-end="140">
<h1 data-section-id="12hgtc" data-start="142" data-end="171">🖼️ STEP 1 — Save the image</h1>
<p data-start="173" data-end="208">From the image I generated for you:</p>
<p data-start="210" data-end="258">👉 Right click → <strong data-start="227" data-end="244">Save image as</strong><br data-start="244" data-end="247">
👉 Name it:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="260" data-end="279"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="複製" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>preview.png</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="281" data-end="284">
<h1 data-section-id="dam3qd" data-start="286" data-end="333">📁 STEP 2 — Upload to your GitHub (IMPORTANT)</h1>
<p data-start="335" data-end="351">Go to your repo:</p>
<p data-start="353" data-end="398">👉 <a data-start="356" data-end="398" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://github.com/youherosr/member-portal<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<hr data-start="400" data-end="403">
<h2 data-section-id="113y22l" data-start="405" data-end="431">🔧 Then follow exactly:</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="12ldq1d" data-start="433" data-end="460"><span role="text">1. Click <strong data-start="446" data-end="460">“Add file”</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="461" data-end="477">(Top right area)</p>
<h3 data-section-id="15y9dmr" data-start="479" data-end="510"><span role="text">2. Click <strong data-start="492" data-end="510">“Upload files”</strong></span></h3>
<h3 data-section-id="1k1okye" data-start="512" data-end="553">3. Drag your image OR click to upload</h3>
<p data-start="554" data-end="577">👉 select <code data-start="564" data-end="577">preview.png</code></p>
<h3 data-section-id="xh32re" data-start="579" data-end="626"><span role="text">4. Scroll down → click <strong data-start="606" data-end="626">“Commit changes”</strong></span></h3>
<hr data-start="628" data-end="631">
<h1 data-section-id="3z3nf6" data-start="633" data-end="665">🔗 STEP 3 — Get your image URL</h1>
<p data-start="667" data-end="680">After upload:</p>
<p data-start="682" data-end="720">👉 Click your image file <code data-start="707" data-end="720">preview.png</code></p>
<p data-start="722" data-end="747">You will see a page like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="748" data-end="820"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="複製" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://github.com/youherosr/member-portal/blob/main/preview.png</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="822" data-end="825">
<h2 data-section-id="1yojo6o" data-start="827" data-end="865">⚠️ IMPORTANT: Convert to PUBLIC URL</h2>
<p data-start="867" data-end="880">Change it to:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="882" data-end="964"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="複製" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/youherosr/member-portal/main/preview.png</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="966" data-end="997">👉 This is the URL you must use</p>
<hr data-start="999" data-end="1002">
<h1 data-section-id="3pbq3z" data-start="1004" data-end="1036">🔧 STEP 4 — Put into your HTML</h1>
<p data-start="1038" data-end="1055">Update this line:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1057" data-end="1180"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="複製" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="編輯"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></div></button></span><div aria-label="切換視圖" class="group relative flex gap-0.5 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-gray-1000"><div aria-hidden="true" class="bg-token-bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute start-0.5 top-0.5 h-8 w-8 rounded-full" style="transform: none;"></div><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="編碼" aria-pressed="true" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-primary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#00f12a" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button type="button" aria-label="預覽" aria-pressed="false" aria-disabled="false" class="relative flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center transition-colors text-token-text-secondary group-hover:text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼg">&lt;meta</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">property</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"og:image"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">content</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/youherosr/member-portal/main/preview.png"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1182" data-end="1185">
<h1 data-section-id="1iisgca" data-start="1187" data-end="1205">🔄 STEP 5 — Test</h1>
<p data-start="1207" data-end="1224">After everything:</p>
<p data-start="1226" data-end="1256">👉 Create a <strong data-start="1238" data-end="1256">NEW Bitly link</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1258" data-end="1261">
<h1 data-section-id="2x7b9t" data-start="1263" data-end="1295">🎯 Example result (after done)</h1>
<p data-start="1297" data-end="1313">Bitly will show:</p>
<ul data-start="1314" data-end="1363">
<li data-section-id="1khf2el" data-start="1314" data-end="1323">
<p data-start="1316" data-end="1323">✅ Title</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1e09d1n" data-start="1324" data-end="1339">
<p data-start="1326" data-end="1339">✅ Description</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15myyzy" data-start="1340" data-end="1363">
<p data-start="1342" data-end="1363">✅ Image (your banner)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1365" data-end="1368">
<h1 data-section-id="aqgq1k" data-start="1370" data-end="1403">❗ Common mistakes (avoid these)</h1>
<p data-start="1405" data-end="1514">❌ Using GitHub URL with <code data-start="1429" data-end="1437">/blob/</code><br data-start="1437" data-end="1440">
❌ Not committing file<br data-start="1461" data-end="1464">
❌ Using wrong path<br data-start="1482" data-end="1485">
❌ Forgetting new Bitly link</p>
<hr data-start="1516" data-end="1519">
<h1 data-section-id="1v85r0x" data-start="1521" data-end="1548">💬 If you want easier way</h1>
<p data-start="1550" data-end="1661">I can:<br>
👉 Generate a <strong data-start="1571" data-end="1626">direct hosted image link for you (no GitHub needed)</strong><br data-start="1626" data-end="1629">
👉 Or guide you with screenshots</p>
<hr data-start="1663" data-end="1666">
<p data-start="1668" data-end="1741">Just tell me:<br>
👉 “show me screenshot guide”<br data-start="1711" data-end="1714">
or<br data-start="1716" data-end="1719">
👉 “host image for me”</p>
